==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Antiattrition
<hw>An`ti*at*tri"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Anything
to prevent the effects of friction, esp. a compound lubricant for
machinery, etc., often consisting of plumbago, with some greasy
material; antifriction grease.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>antiauthoritarian</ent>⟦br⟧
